snippet.title: Holfraine - Announce Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Holfraine is exclusively on PlayStation 4, out on March 3rd. Hero Shooter. 3 VS 3. New Game Mode with dynamic events. 

Song Featured "Holfraine Theme" by Bayle Music.

Holfraine has a new hero shooter mode, All-In-1. This new game mode includes dynamic events, missions and changing characters through the match. Choose among a wide variety of skins.
Play and be the best!

Developed by FluXart studio with the support of PlayStation Talents.
